\v 30 Moses left Pharaoh and prayed to the Lord,
\v 31 and the Lord did as Moses asked, and removed the swarms of flies from Pharaoh and his officials and his people. Not \w a|strong="H3068"\w* single fly remained.
\v 32 But once again Pharaoh chose to be stubbornly hard-hearted and would not let the people leave.
