\v 11 then \w an|strong="H1589"\w* oath must be taken \w before|strong="H5973"\w* \w the|strong="H5973"\w* Lord \w to|strong="H5973"\w* decide if \w the|strong="H5973"\w* neighbor \w has|strong="H5973"\w* taken \w the|strong="H5973"\w* \w owner|strong="H1167"\w*'s property. \w The|strong="H5973"\w* \w owner|strong="H1167"\w* must accept \w the|strong="H5973"\w* oath \w and|strong="H5973"\w* not demand compensation.
\p 
\v 12 However, if \w the|strong="H3808"\w* \w animal|strong="H2966"\w* really \w was|strong="H3808"\w* stolen \w from|strong="H3808"\w* \w the|strong="H3808"\w* neighbor, \w he|strong="H3808"\w* \w must|strong="H3808"\w* compensate \w the|strong="H3808"\w* owner.
\v 13 \w If|strong="H3588"\w* \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w was|strong="H7592"\w* \w killed|strong="H4191"\w* \w and|strong="H4191"\w* \w torn|strong="H7665"\w* \w to|strong="H4191"\w* \w pieces|strong="H7665"\w* \w by|strong="H4191"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wild animal, \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w neighbor|strong="H7453"\w* \w shall|strong="H7453"\w* \w present|strong="H7999"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* carcass \w as|strong="H3588"\w* evidence \w and|strong="H4191"\w* does \w not|strong="H3588"\w* need \w to|strong="H4191"\w* \w pay|strong="H7999"\w* compensation.
\p 
\v 14 \w If|strong="H1931"\w* someone borrows \w a|strong="H3068"\w* neighbor's animal \w and|strong="H5973"\w* \w it|strong="H1931"\w*'s injured \w or|strong="H3808"\w* dies \w while|strong="H1931"\w* \w its|strong="H1167"\w* \w owner|strong="H1167"\w* \w is|strong="H1931"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w present|strong="H7999"\w*, \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w must|strong="H3808"\w* \w pay|strong="H7999"\w* \w compensation|strong="H7939"\w* \w in|strong="H3808"\w* \w full|strong="H7999"\w*.
\v 15 \w If|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* owner \w was|strong="H3808"\w* present, \w no|strong="H3808"\w* compensation \w is|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H5973"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* paid. \w If|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* animal \w was|strong="H3808"\w* hired, \w only|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* hire charge needs \w to|strong="H5973"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* paid.
\p 
\v 16 If \w a|strong="H3068"\w* man seduces \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w virgin|strong="H1330"\w* who \w is|strong="H3701"\w* \w not|strong="H5414"\w* engaged \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w be|strong="H5414"\w* married \w and|strong="H3701"\w* sleeps \w with|strong="H3701"\w* \w her|strong="H5414"\w*, \w he|strong="H5414"\w* must \w pay|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* full bride-price \w for|strong="H5414"\w* \w her|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5414"\w* become \w his|strong="H5414"\w* wife.
\v 17 If her father adamantly refuses \w to|strong="H2421"\w* \w give|strong="H2421"\w* her \w to|strong="H2421"\w* \w him|strong="H2421"\w*, \w the|strong="H3808"\w* man still \w must|strong="H3808"\w* pay \w the|strong="H3808"\w* same amount as \w the|strong="H3808"\w* bride-price \w for|strong="H2421"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* virgin.
\p 
\v 18 \w You|strong="H3605"\w* \w must|strong="H4191"\w* \w not|strong="H4191"\w* allow \w a|strong="H3068"\w* woman \w who|strong="H3605"\w* practices witchcraft \w to|strong="H4191"\w* live.
\p 
\v 19 Anyone \w who|strong="H3068"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* sex \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w an|strong="H3068"\w* animal must \w be|strong="H3068"\w* executed.
\p 
\v 20 \w Anyone|strong="H3588"\w* \w who|strong="H1616"\w* sacrifices \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w any|strong="H1961"\w* other \w god|strong="H3808"\w* \w than|strong="H3808"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* Lord \w must|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* set apart \w and|strong="H4714"\w* executed.\f + \fr 22:20 \ft “Set apart and executed”: the term used here means “devoted to destruction” in the sense they now are to suffer God's punishment.\f*
\p 
\v 21 \w You|strong="H3605"\w* \w must|strong="H3808"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* exploit \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w mistreat|strong="H6031"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* foreigner. Remember \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w yourselves|strong="H3605"\w* \w were|strong="H3605"\w* once foreigners \w in|strong="H3808"\w* Egypt.
\p 
\v 22 \w You|strong="H3588"\w* must \w not|strong="H3588"\w* take advantage \w of|strong="H8085"\w* \w any|strong="H6031"\w* widow \w or|strong="H8085"\w* orphan.
\v 23 \w If|strong="H1961"\w* \w you|strong="H1961"\w* mistreat \w them|strong="H2026"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w they|strong="H2719"\w* call out \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H2026"\w* \w for|strong="H1121"\w* \w help|strong="H1961"\w*, \w I|strong="H1121"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* definitely respond \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w their|strong="H1961"\w* cry.
\v 24 \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w become|strong="H1961"\w* angry, \w and|strong="H3701"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* kill \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* sword. \w Your|strong="H5921"\w* wives \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w become|strong="H1961"\w* \w widows|strong="H5971"\w* \w and|strong="H3701"\w* \w your|strong="H5921"\w* children \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* fatherless.
\p 
\v 25 If \w you|strong="H5704"\w* lend money \w to|strong="H5704"\w* any \w of|strong="H7725"\w* \w my|strong="H7725"\w* people because \w they|strong="H5704"\w*'re poor, \w you|strong="H5704"\w* must \w not|strong="H7725"\w* behave \w as|strong="H5704"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* moneylender \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w them|strong="H7725"\w*. \w You|strong="H5704"\w* must \w not|strong="H7725"\w* charge \w them|strong="H7725"\w* any interest.
